Text: 'Herman Cape is a factory worker in UK who lost his job. His woman has a lover
  and take  her husband out of home.

  Herman, alone and without money, sell his kidney to win money to escape from his
  live. But he sick.

  Forgotten in a hospital, he knows a female patient. They travel in her camping car
  from Barcelona to Tarifa, change their lives, growth spiritually. There, in the
  southest part of Europe, they die'
